Package nl.naturalis.oaipmh.geneious

OAI Repositories for providing data from Geneious.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAnnotatedDocumentPostFilter
    Filters records from the annotated_document table after they have been converted to AnnotatedDocument instances.
    IAnnotatedDocumentPreFilter
    Filters records from the annotated_document table before they are converted from raw ResultSet data to AnnotatedDocument instances.
    IAnnotatedDocumentSetFilter
    A set filter takes an entire set of AnnotatedDocument instances in order to get rid of discardable ones.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ABIDocument
    Models the contents of the plugin_document_xml column in case the root element is <ABIDocument>.
    ABIDocumentFactory
    Factory for ABIDocument instances.
    AnnotatedDocument
    Models a record in the annotated_document table.
    AnnotatedDocumentFactory
    A factory for AnnotatedDocument instances.
    DatabaseIDComparator
    A Comparator for AnnotatedDocument instances that selects the instance with the highest database ID.
    DefaultAlignmentDocument
    Models the contents of the plugin_document_xml column in case the root element is <DefaultAlignmentDocument>.
    DefaultAlignmentDocumentFactory
    A factory for DefaultAlignmentDocument instances.
    Document
    Standard Java Bean reflecting the contents of the document_xml column within the annotated_document table.
    DocumentFactory
    A factory for Document instances.
    DocumentNotes
    A DocumentNotes instance maintains the values of all relevant notes within the document_xml column.
    DocumentVersionComparator
    A Comparator for AnnotatedDocument instances that, extract ID and marker being equal, selects the instance with the highest document version.
    GeneiousOAIRepository
    Abstract base class for all Geneious OAI repositories.
    GeneiousOAIUtil
    Provides common functionality for Geneious OAI repositories.
    ListRecordsHandler
    Abstract base class for handlers for the ListRecords protocol request.
    PluginDocument
    Abstract base class for all classes modeling the contents of the plugin_document_xml column of the annotated_document table.
    ReferenceComparator Deprecated
    SharedPostFilter
    Post-filter shared by all geneious repositories.
    SharedPreFilter
    Pre-filter shared by all geneious repositories.
    SharedSetFilter
    Set filter shared by all geneious repositories.
    XMLSerialisableRootElement
    Models the contents of the plugin_document_xml column in case the root element is <XMLSerialisableRootElement>.
    XMLSerialisableRootElementFactory
    Factory for XMLSerialisableRootElement instances.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DocumentClass
    An enumeration of a possible values for the "class" attribute of the <document> element in the document_xml column.
    DocumentNotes.Note
    Enumerates all XML elements that contain a note that might be used for OAI-PMH generation.
